  <brief_title>Safety and Feasibility of Arrhythmia Ablation Using the Amigo Remote Robotic System as Compared With Manual Ablation</brief_title>
  <official_title>Safety and Feasibility of Arrhythmia Ablation Using the Amigo Remote Robotic System as Compared With Manual Ablation</official_title>
